<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.6.5">
<l>piccacci ṟupīlic camaṇkuṇṭar mutalāyōr</l>
<l>viccaikki ṟaiyeṉṉu mavviṟaiyaip paṇiyātē</l>
<l>kaccikki ṭantavaṉūr kaṭaṉmallait talacayaṉam</l>
<l>naccitto ḻuvārai nacceṉṟaṉ naṉṉeñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without bowing to that god who is called the god of knowledge</l>
<l>[By], first of all, the Jain wretches with little peacock fans,</l>
<l>My own good heart, love those who lovingly worship</l>
<l>At Talacayaṉam at Mallai by the sea, the city of him who lies in Kacci.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
